Cursor Setup Assignment

What tools you installed
Cursor IDE
GitHub
Anthropic API integration (connected through API key)

What steps you completed
Installed Cursor IDE.
Created a public GitHub repository.
Opened the repository in Cursor.
Researched how to connect Anthropic and OpenAI services when the Claude Code and Codex extensions were not available in the current Cursor Marketplace.
Connected Anthropic API access in Cursor Settings.
Connected OpenAI API access in Cursor Settings.

Issues Encountered

** Claude Code and Codex extensions were not available

I searched for "Claude Code" and "Codex" in the current Cursor Marketplace but could not find either extension.

To solve this issue, I researched alternative methods and found that Cursor allows direct integration through Anthropic and OpenAI API keys in the Settings > Models section.

As a workaround, I connected both services using API keys instead of installing marketplace extensions.
